01:06:09.289 --> 01:06:10.289
for like microbrewers, or they can't go national
they get bought out sometimes and you have

01:06:10.289 --> 01:06:11.289
unintended consequences that come about from
that -- from globalization itself.

01:06:11.289 --> 01:06:12.289
And then, finally, we get to the liquor market.
Distilled spirits, of course, like I said,

01:06:12.289 --> 01:06:13.289
they hit the wall back in the 1970s.
And just in the last decade, they've been

01:06:13.289 --> 01:06:14.289
resurrected, and I kind of chart the beginning
of distilled spirits -- of the phenomenon

01:06:14.289 --> 01:06:15.289
 -- to Sex in the City.
So any fans here of the show?

01:06:15.289 --> 01:06:16.289
The girls on the show really made the cosmopolitan
popular, like really glamorous.

01:06:16.289 --> 01:06:17.289
They always used to change their outfits all
