01:06:17.289 --> 01:06:18.289
pink fruity martini that they drink when they
would go out.

01:06:18.289 --> 01:06:19.289
And Americans kind of caught on to that like,
"Wow, spirits -- like really cool, right?"

01:06:19.289 --> 01:06:20.289
So I kind of chart that as the beginning of
the resurrection here for distilled spirits.

01:06:20.289 --> 01:06:21.289
And you get to today, there's this huge craft
cocktail phenomenon going on.

01:06:21.289 --> 01:06:22.289
So if you go into San Francisco, or local
bars, where you have these -- I call them

01:06:22.289 --> 01:06:23.289
'culinary bartenders' who take their inspiration
