01:06:25.289 --> 01:06:26.289
and spices and stuff like that into cocktails.
So there's been this really huge shift.

01:06:26.289 --> 01:06:27.289
And cocktails, of course, you can do an infinite
variety of types of drinks here that you can

01:06:27.289 --> 01:06:28.289
make.
So really a significant shift here that's

01:06:28.289 --> 01:06:29.289
happened just within the last decade.
So it's kind of interesting here to look.

01:06:29.289 --> 01:06:30.289
You also, of course, have the craft phenomenon
going on within distilled spirits itself.

01:06:30.289 --> 01:06:31.289
They're kind of the last ones that have got
there.

01:06:31.289 --> 01:06:32.289
And it's just happened just in the last couple
of years.

01:06:32.289 --> 01:06:33.289
This particular photo right here is Winford
Reserve.

01:06:33.289 --> 01:06:34.289
I was just out there just last month here
giving a talk.

01:06:34.289 --> 01:06:35.289
But yeah, you think the word Winford Reserve.
It sounds like a wine, doesn't it?

01:06:35.289 --> 01:06:36.289
It's a brand that was great in 1996, and yet
