01:08:20.289 --> 01:08:21.289
always been allowed for TV.
The debate over advertising has gone on since

01:08:21.289 --> 01:08:22.289
the 1930's when the WCTU and other organizations
that were heavily involved in temperance wanted

01:08:22.289 --> 01:08:23.289
to stop all advertising altogether.
